    "title": [
      "Direction mutation pressure of SARS-CoV-2 helps to understand the past and predict the future evolution: C&gt;U and G&gt;U biased mutagenesis forces the majority of amino-acid substitutions to be from CG-rich losers to U-rich gainers"
